exercises.notes: On set 3: Complete 12-15 reps, drop the weight by 10-20%, get as many reps as possible. Then drop the weight by a further 10-20% and get as many reps as possible.

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Press
exercises.notes: On set 3: Complete 10-14 reps, rest 20 seconds, then complete as many reps as possible.

exercises.name: Cable Crossover
exercises.notes: On set 3: use a weight you could get around 15 reps with. Complete 12 reps, rest 20s, complete 8 reps, rest 20s then complete as many reps as possible.

exercises.name: Barbell bent Over Row
exercises.notes: On set 3: complete 10-14 reps, drop the weight by 20-30% and complete as many reps as possible.

exercises.name: Standing Reverse Cable Fly
exercises.notes: On set 2 only: Pause in the squeeze for 2-3s on each rep.

exercises.name: Wide Grip Lat Pulldown
exercises.notes: Set 3 is a muscle round: Use the same weight as set 2, then complete as many rounds of 6 reps, rest 10s as possible. The set ends when you cannot complete 6 reps.
